videos.description: Jonathan Isaac throws down a huge alley-oop dunk to open the game for Florida State.
videos.headline: Isaac alley-oop has FSU off to explosive start

videos.description: Clemson's Jaron Blossomgame throws it down over contesting defenders.
videos.headline: Blossomgame rocks the rim with huge throwdown

videos.description: Avry Holmes knocks down a jumper off an ankle breaking move.
videos.headline: Holmes leaves his defender on the ground after slick move

videos.description: Donte Grantham throws down the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Grantham throws it down off the alley-oop

videos.description: Christ Koumadje slams it home off the alley-oop from Terance Mann.
videos.headline: Mann assists on another big alley-oop

videos.description: Michael Ojo throws down dunks on back to back possessions
videos.headline: Ojo dunks twice for Florida State

videos.description: Jonathan Isaac gets a clutch block to keep Clemson from taking a late lead.
videos.headline: Isaac gets big block in key situation

videos.description: Marcquise Reed comes up short on a last chance effort as Clemson loses to Florida State.
videos.headline: Clemson last chance comes up short for Reed

videos.description: Xavier Rathan-Mayes talks about Florida State's effort in their 76-74 road win over Clemson
videos.headline: FSU's Rathan-Mayes postgame interview
